{"tid":657998,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【天真過天真嬌】內地漢稱千元人仔包的士 的士狗誤信反被呃 $500!?","createTime":"2018-05-08T14:33:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-08T15:30:58.000Z","uid":2547,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a8ce09816e03d8158cc2d7a754d69895ceba569e","tid":657998,"uid":2547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T14:33:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/KFYOYYQ8_D0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FKFYOYYQ8_D0&d=GtAXJ63CH5ngc%2FoJJJ3mSkjIoeaDRyeQRMy%2FzT52C%2Fo%3D&h=2a40d27b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/KFYOYYQ8_D0</a><br />\n<br />\n從網上流傳的車 cam 日期顯示，事件發生於上周四 ( 3 日 ) 下午近五時，當時一名夜更司機於街頭接載一名滿口鄉音的男子，對方甫上車便問司機是否開夜班，司機稱是後對方顯得非常雀躍，並指要到上水火車站接載一班道士到紅磡的殯儀館打齋，又聲稱以 1,300 元人民幣包車至晚上十一時，的士司機亦答應交易。<br />\n<br />\n不過途中這名男乘客卻忽然要求先改到沙田，表示要回家「攞聖經」，又指到沙田後會先給對方 200 元人民幣，的士司機於是改往沙水，又要求對方先給自己 1,300 元人民幣，不過乘客表示現時沒有錢在身，要到上水站後才能給錢，司機不疑有詐繼續開車。<br />\n的士下午約五時十五分到達沙田，這名男乘客下車時半催半請的情況下向司機借了 500 元港幣，隨即下車，聲稱自己很快就會回來，司機給錢後一直在沙田廣場門外等候，最後當然等不到這位男乘客出現。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 未見過咁撚蠢既人"},{"pid":"175c24e6029dd8f3d9675260df9ed88515326542","tid":657998,"uid":48973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T15:02:14.000Z","msg":"作為道士打齋羅本聖經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"